13:09.748 --> 13:11.249
<i>I'm an average dude.</i>

13:11.291 --> 13:12.792
<i>You know, they think</i>
<i>Olympians, and there's, like,</i>

13:12.834 --> 13:15.295
<i>this normal-looking dude</i>
