14:05.762 --> 14:08.181
Mm.
Delicious.

14:08.223 --> 14:09.849
<i>Why do I want to go back</i>
<i>to the Olympics?</i>

14:09.891 --> 14:14.104
<i>Well, I mean, I just felt like</i>
<i>I just still loved curling.</i>

14:14.145 --> 14:16.231
<i>I don't think</i>
<i>I'm ready to give up</i>

14:16.272 --> 14:18.149
<i>this, like, lifestyle.</i>

14:18.191 --> 14:19.984
<i>So I had a talk with the wife,</i>

14:20.026 --> 14:22.529
<i>and she's like, run it back.</i>

14:22.570 --> 14:24.531
<i>So here I am.</i>

14:25.907 --> 14:27.409
- Aw, I hit the top there.
- Whoa.

14:40.839 --> 14:42.841
Oof. I'm sprayin' 'em.

14:42.882 --> 14:46.594
Now everybody watching
