Broke a lotta brooms, um,

17:09.738 --> 17:13.491
used to have a little bit
more of a mouth.

17:13.533 --> 17:14.993
<i>Just something I realized that</i>

17:15.035 --> 17:17.704
<i>even if I saw it as something</i>
<i>that was helping me,</i>

17:17.746 --> 17:20.248
<i>it may not have been</i>
<i>for the greater good,</i>

17:20.290 --> 17:22.334
<i>and so something</i>
<i>I had to work on.</i>

