<i>with a job or stress.</i>

17:45.899 --> 17:48.735
<i>It's easy to let</i>
<i>all that stuff go out here.</i>

17:53.448 --> 17:56.576
<i>- Plys will tell you</i>
<i>he's mellowed some--</i>

17:56.618 --> 17:59.371
<i>personal growth</i>
<i>that served him well</i>

17:59.412 --> 18:01.915
<i>as the new guy</i>
<i>expected to perform</i>

18:01.956 --> 18:04.584
<i>like a defending</i>
<i>gold medalist.</i>

18:06.086 --> 18:08.004
<i>- It's definitely</i>
<i>a pressure cooker.</i>

18:08.046 --> 18:10.090
<i>I didn't wanna,</i>
<i>you know, come in</i>

18:10.131 --> 18:12.008
<i>and try and blow up</i>
<i>other team systems</i>

18:12.050 --> 18:13.968
<i>and all that kinda stuff,</i>
<i>so it took a little time</i>

18:14.010 --> 18:15.595
<i>to find my spot</i>

18:15.637 --> 18:17.555
<i>where I felt comfortable</i>
<i>going out on the ice</i>

18:17.597 --> 18:20.016
<i>every single time.</i>

18:20.058 --> 18:22.477
<i>Those guys have had</i>
<i>a lot more opportunity</i>

18:22.519 --> 18:24.145
<i>to play in like</i>
<i>those big games,</i>

18:24.187 --> 18:26.064
<i>so any big game that I get</i>
<i>a chance to play in,</i>

18:26.106 --> 18:27.857
<i>like I'm just stoked</i>
<i>to get on the ice,</i>

18:27.899 --> 18:30.443
and I just like to get
out there and compete.

18:31.236 --> 18:35.240
<i>- Last April, the journey</i>
<i>to the 2022 Olympics</i>

18:35.281 --> 18:38.910
<i>began with the World</i>
<i>Championships in Calgary.</i>

18:38.952 --> 18:42.789
<i>The revamped foursome needed</i>
<i>to get to the quarterfinals</i>

18:42.831 --> 18:45.083
<i>to earn the United States</i>
<i>a guaranteed spot</i>

18:45.125 --> 18:47.002
<i>at the Olympics--</i>

18:47.043 --> 18:50.505
<i>high stakes for which Plys</i>
<i>and his teammates</i>

18:50.547 --> 18:52.215
<i>looked more than ready.</i>

18:53.133 --> 18:55.635
- I've always prided myself
on being a shot maker.

18:55.677 --> 18:57.887
<i>I just kinda sit back</i>
<i>and make shots,</i>

18:57.929 --> 18:59.431
be there for the guys
when they need it,

18:59.472 --> 19:01.474
sweep hard.

19:01.516 --> 19:03.727
<i>- Look at this!</i>
<i>Doesn't get better than that.</i>

19:05.437 --> 19:06.896
<i>If you watch any game,</i>

19:06.938 --> 19:09.899
we were having the most fun
of any team on the ice.

