- <i>Need something special.</i>
- Go, hard! Forget it.

23:02.132 --> 23:03.216
Forget it, guys.

23:03.258 --> 23:04.676
- Forget it.
- All right, all right.

23:04.718 --> 23:07.387
<i>That will not get it done,</i>

23:07.429 --> 23:09.723
<i>and this hard-fought battle</i>
<i>will be pulled out</i>

23:09.764 --> 23:13.226
- <i>by team Switzerland.</i>
- Continued good luck.

23:13.268 --> 23:16.730
<i>- It was an odd,</i>
<i>almost contradictory blend</i>

23:16.771 --> 23:19.315
<i>of satisfaction</i>
<i>and disappointment...</i>

23:19.357 --> 23:22.485
<i>mixed in with</i>
<i>the not-unimportant fact</i>

23:22.527 --> 23:25.780
<i>that they'd done what they</i>
<i>needed to get done.</i>

23:25.822 --> 23:28.324
<i>The U.S. had a spot</i>
<i>at the Olympics.</i>

