<i>And with the U.S. trials</i>

23:32.162 --> 23:33.955
<i>a little more</i>
<i>than six months away,</i>

23:33.997 --> 23:35.999
<i>maybe most important</i>

23:36.041 --> 23:38.710
<i>was something</i>
<i>that couldn't be quantified--</i>

23:38.752 --> 23:43.256
<i>the team's bond was as tightly</i>
<i>sealed as it'd ever been.</i>

23:43.298 --> 23:47.469
<i>No matter the field of play,</i>
<i>if this foursome was together,</i>

23:47.510 --> 23:50.889
<i>they were at least</i>
<i>gonna have some fun.</i>

