Keeping a tee shot left will
give you a better approach

24:02.108 --> 24:04.110
into this makeable,
scorable green.

24:04.152 --> 24:05.653
- Mike, are you reading
something,

24:05.695 --> 24:07.947
- or is that like legitimate--
