24:07.989 --> 24:10.033
- That's pretty fantastic,
Matthew.

24:11.826 --> 24:13.495
- Oh, that's going--
- And...breakfast.

24:13.536 --> 24:15.372
Breakfast balls.

24:16.164 --> 24:19.292
<i>- All good teams move forward</i>
<i>after defeats.</i>

24:19.334 --> 24:21.211
Mashed potatoes!

24:21.252 --> 24:24.756
<i>- They recover,</i>
<i>they decompress,</i>

24:24.798 --> 24:28.218
<i>and then they recharge.</i>

