Our goal is to go back
to the Olympics

24:31.763 --> 24:34.391
to defend that gold medal
that those guys won.

24:34.432 --> 24:36.309
<i>So come Olympic trials,</i>
<i>you know,</i>

24:36.351 --> 24:39.312
<i>I can't think of many things</i>
<i>that could really top</i>

24:39.354 --> 24:41.147
<i>what was thrown at us</i>
<i>at the World's.</i>

24:41.189 --> 24:43.149
<i>so I think it'll put us</i>
<i>in a really great position,</i>

24:43.191 --> 24:46.069
you know, when we get to Omaha
in November.

24:46.111 --> 24:47.696
A real subtle putter.

24:50.782 --> 24:52.200
That's pretty sharp, right?

24:52.242 --> 24:54.911
- Aah!

24:56.871 --> 24:59.457
- Well, I'll get on the green.
